{"tid":2054930,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"痴撚線？呢個台灣圍棋女棋士極有氣質！！！（有片）","createTime":"2020-06-07T14:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T02:07:04.000Z","uid":118346,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5c1fde33dc0a1b5353ee5b1dad7520e01a9cdd6a","tid":2054930,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T14:06:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tX3WUtHytyw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtX3WUtHytyw&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUo26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=aa0de63b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tX3WUtHytyw</a><br />\n<br />\n2008年7月，黑嘉嘉在中國大陸第二度挑戰定段賽，取得第2名的成績，獲得職業初段資格。是目前台灣第一位，也是唯一在中國大陸入段的職業女棋士，因選擇保留中華民國與澳洲國籍，沒有申請加入中國國籍，也沒有在中國棋院註冊。2010年取得台灣棋院初段資格，在台灣棋院註冊。2012年被選為世界圍棋形象大使。<br />\n<br />\n目前黑嘉嘉擁有中國棋院職業初段資格，台灣棋院職業七段棋士。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2681d611add7a393421dddfd198d049d99e3e6da","tid":2054930,"uid":118346,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T14:07:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/jiajia94526/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fjiajia94526%2F&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUo26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=41a87928\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/jiajia94526/</a><br />\n<br />\nIG 相極 gfable"},{"pid":"eff24cad1c39bbfd457f49542641d49bc9706409","tid":2054930,"uid":277186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T14:08:43.000Z","msg":"Dllm我以前棋藝社成班毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" cla